modShortDescription: Similar to the stove mod this adds sinks and water coolers you can upgrade in the 7 Days to Die world and use to fill jars and buckets.
modDescription:
Similar to the [stove mod](https://7daystodiemods.com/working-stove-mod-for-a18/) this adds sinks and water coolers you can upgrade in the 7 Days to Die world and use to fill jars and buckets.

[Download](https://yehonal.github.io/DownGit/#/home?url=https://github.com/JaxTeller718/JaxTeller718_Modlets_Stable/tree/master/JaxTeller718_WorkingSinksAndCoolers)

If you appreciate JaxTeller718’s work here feel free to use this [donate link](https://www.paypal.me/FrankCirabisiJr) to show support.

The forum topic of the mod is [here](https://community.7daystodie.com/topic/8098-jaxteller718-modlet-collection/).

**Credits:** [JaxTeller718](https://7daystodiemods.com/tag/jaxteller718/)
